{
  "stem": "4189.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was done with the help of these women that worked there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, the SS guards knew that the only place where they could have gotten this dynamite was from our factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they took these girls-- there was four of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They tortured them terribly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they would not reveal whom they gave the dynamite to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, finally, they took these four girls and they hung them, in front of the entire factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had to watch them hanging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Two girls-- on was Esther, and one was Rosa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The other one, the other two I don't remember the names, offhand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But two were hanged in the morning tour, and two were hanged in the evening tour.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that everybody was able to watch them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Their faces were unrecognizable from the tortures that they received from the interrogations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was only now that the Auschwitz committee was able to get permission from Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was now in-- 19-- I believe it was a few years ago, in 1989, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They erected a monument in Yad Vashem for those four girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We-- we collected-- we all contributed money to get a-- a architect, a stonemason, to make a monument of those four girls-- those four heroes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that monument is now in Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then-- we-- then-- soon-- this incident happened in-- in 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe it was in October of 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a few months later, in January of 1944, the Russian army in the east had advanced so far that he could hear, already, the artillery shells bursting.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We heard the-- the-- you know, we heard the shooting in the distance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they decided to evacuate Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on January 18, 1945, Auschwitz was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started to march.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
